@Node "Model 1"

 @{b}Model 1@{ub}

 @{" Scanline Render " system "Run multiview IM:Pics/Mod1.iff"}

  This object was made by me in a hurry to finish a quick job I was asked to
 do for a friend (if you think its that lame, send it some yourself).

  Its a FireFight Mk II long range attack jet (space of course). This is the
 "armed" object (notice the weapons). I haven't had time to fix the AWLFUL
 colours of the jet, but still. Its made out of 100% primitives, but resized
 etc. Its a pretty good jet, but needs a bit of work.

  This object was made with Imagine 3, I now use Imagine 5 of course.

  My previous work of these was much better, but this is a quicky...

