@Node "Model 2"

 @{b}Model 2@{ub}

 @{" Trace " system "Run Multiview IM:Pics/Mod2.iff"}

  This object was made by me, and is a layout of a dining table and bg. The
 textures used are fully digitized, as the ones supplied with Imagine weren't
 good enough. The flame was drawn by hand afterwards.

  The chairs are just flat disks, and the walls are just as easy, the light
 sources actually are on the candles, plus another one hidden away that doesn't
 cast a shadow...

  You can have lots of fun if you put the Shredder (Imagine 5) or Explode
 effect on it, SLOW, but good fun.

  This was, made all in primitives (slightly cut etc)

